$$
\begin{align*}
\sum M_{O_1} &= M_{k_1} + M_{G_1} - M_{\theta_1}\\
&= r_{k_1} \times F_{k_1} + r_{G_1} \times G_1 - J_1 \alpha_1 \\
&= \frac{1}{2} m_1 g L -\frac{9}{16} 3 k_1 L^2 \theta_1+\frac{9}{16} k_1 L^2 \theta_2-\frac{1}{3} m_1 L^2 \ddot \theta_1\\
&=0
\end{align*}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe center; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 555px; margin-left: 600px;

div.data-content:
$$
\begin{cases}
r_{k_1} &= (\frac{3 L}{4},0) \\
F_{k_1} &= (0,-k_1 \left(\frac{3 L}{4} \theta_1-\frac{3 L}{4} \theta_2\right)) \\
r_{G_1} &= (\frac{L}{2},0) \\
{G_1} &= (0, m_1 g) \\
J_1 &= \frac{m_1 L^2 }{3} \\
\alpha_1 &= \ddot \theta_1
\end{cases}
$$

div.data-content:
$$
\begin{align*}
\sum M_{O_2} &= M_{k_2} + M_{k_2} + M_{G_1} - M_{\theta_1}\\
&= r_{k_1} \times F_{k_1} + r_{k_2} \times F_{k_2} + r_{G_2} \times G_2 - J_2 \alpha_2 \\
&= \frac{1}{4}m_2 g L + \frac{9}{16} k_1 L^2 \theta_1-\frac{9}{16} k_1 L^2 \theta_2-\frac{1}{4} k_2 L^2 \theta_2-\frac{7}{48}m_2 L^2 \ddot \theta_2\\
&=0
\end{align*}
$$

哈密顿原理

$$\int \delta T + \delta W = 0$$

$$
\begin{cases}
T &= \frac {1} {2} J_1 \dot \theta_1^2 + \frac {1} {2} J_2 \dot \theta_2^2\\
W &= \frac {1} {2} k_1 \Delta x_1^2 + \frac {1} {2} k_2 \Delta x_2^2 + m_1 g \frac{L}{2} \theta_1 + m_2 g \frac{L}{4} \theta_2
\end{cases}
$$

\begin{cases}
\frac{1}{48} L \left(8 m_1 \left(3 g-2 L \ddot \theta_1\right)+27 k_1 L \left(\theta_1-\theta_2\right)\right)=0 \\
\frac{1}{48} L \left(m_2 \left(12 g-7 L \ddot \theta_2\right)+3 L \left(4 k_2 \theta_2-9 k_1 \left(\theta_1-\theta_2\right)\right)\right)=0
\end{cases}
$$
